author: USA TODAY, Kim Hjelmgaard, USA TODAY
title: WHO says coronavirus came from an animal and was not made in a lab
description: The Trump administration is probing whether coronavirus originated in a lab. There is no evidence it did. The WHO says it came from an animal.
content:
When will it hit and what will it look like? Those are just a few unanswered questions about a possible second wave of COVID-19.
USA TODAY
All the available evidence indicates coronavirus originated in animals in China late last year and was not manipulated… [+3054 chars]
